body_html: Judging from the error, you are attempting to use Dataset.batch() on a dataset of elements with different shapes. If the elements have different shapes, you must either (i) transform them to all have the same shape (e.g. using Dataset.map()) or (ii) use Dataset.padded_batch() to add padding to some of the components.

body: Judging from the error, you are attempting to use `Dataset.batch()` on a dataset of elements with different shapes. If the elements have different shapes, you must either (i) transform them to all have the same shape (e.g. using `Dataset.map()`) or (ii) use `Dataset.padded_batch()` to add padding to some of the components.
